OL,7,BMARCH AGAINST BLOOD SPORTS    CAugust 2
OL,8, The National Anti-Hunt League is asking
OL,9, you to join them in a march against    
OL,10, blood sports. Meet at noon, Reformers  
OL,11, Tree, Hyde Park for a trek to Trafalgar
OL,12, Square in London.                      
OL,14, The League is also holding an          
OL,15, exhibition on the same day detailing   
OL,16, the "horrors" of blood sports at       
OL,17, Westminster Central Hall, Storey's     
OL,18, Gate, London, SW1, from 10am till 8pm. 
